  <title>Add Transition Curve</title>
  <meta name="DESCRIPTION" translate="true" value="A Transition-Curve is used to eliminate Polygonal Action with Chains.It is good all the way down to 3 teeth on the sprocket. There is not versiation in Velocity or Tension in the Chain as it travels around the Track." />
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Add<keyword>Transition-Curve</keyword></keyword>
